{"tid":1395992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論] 往後的星期六 ,日遊行示威的策略","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:58:17.000Z","uid":94771,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"60178ba6b6c048ba2fc1adfb631fb669682812d6","tid":1395992,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:50:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家認真討論 唔好太比主觀感覺影響到自己 <br />\n好老實我好迷網 唔知點先對個運動最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>繼續依家條勇武路線 每次都活動完後守路 :</strong><br />\n<strong>好處:</strong><br />\n1. 可以再比壓力警犬<br />\n2. 增加犬犯錯機會<br />\n3. 令政府感到壓力<br />\n4. 象徵意義<br />\n5. 運動不同意義上的保溫 不論好壞<br />\n<br />\n<strong>壞處:</strong><br />\n1. 勇武手足被捕 而且全部會被司法迫害<br />\n2. 勇武手足受傷 警犬更強的武力<br />\n3. 令淺黃,中立對衝突畫面厭倦 變到 不參與及後活動 (變成花生派)<br />\n4. 佔多數的和理非示威人數因害怕衝突及控罪減少<br />\n5. 運動續戰力較差 比較難把運動拉長 因為愈來愈多人被捕 同 和理非變花生派<br />\n<br />\n<strong>暫時轉做和理非 遊完慢慢散水 :</strong><br />\n<strong>好處:</strong><br />\n1. 令多數的和理非示威人數可以增加返 運動可以回氣<br />\n2. 令中立派轉向更加針對政府<br />\n3. 運動的續戰力可以拉長<br />\n4. 依邊的手足唔會犯錯 輿論戰取場得優勢(輿論戰上)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>壞處:</strong><br />\n1. 對政府的施壓力較細<br />\n2. 警犬壓力比較上無咁大<br />\n3. 有保溫能力，但畫面無咁震撼<br />\n<br />\n<strong>個人意見</strong><br />\n依個星期可以轉返做和理非表態同通碟　之後政府唔理就返去勇武路線。<br />\n一星期和理非　一星期勇武　不斷做通碟<br />\n盡量將戰線持續到10月1 搞高人數大遊行 落9共慘黨70周年面"},{"pid":"3ceaef55cfdf624bfe24476a8439784689337933","tid":1395992,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562fc16387e7b66df56fd52ed381fd62a6586cad","tid":1395992,"uid":12018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25879b077be3e35a92647d74185c6cacc9876f1c","tid":1395992,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以討論<br />\n發現無咩人做大方向的討論POST<br />\n好多人對及後的運動 目標方向好亂"},{"pid":"7fdbadc90286e119ae70d02aa1318cc3e808d084","tid":1395992,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iz0C2NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz0C2NO.jpg&h=26f6cd28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEfzkzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEfzkzy.jpg&h=2457788e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab86f7a9f466c65bdc9ee01df369ced2bac93811","tid":1395992,"uid":199640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:56:25.000Z","msg":"問題係D犬主動攻擊，點解一次和理非一次勇武呀"},{"pid":"6f6b2bdd2abb1627bd8d346767d5f6df24d6ef0d","tid":1395992,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"想玩狗狗就玩狗狗，唔駛揾藉口。<br />\n🦴🦴🦴"},{"pid":"a126a10eb4e6e67e2e2fc05e495f6444ac909d90","tid":1395992,"uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"唔set防線 同主動扔狗 就無事<br />\n<br />\n出到去做文宣就話全部係警犬引起衝突先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角就係集會結束佐都不斷向前行<br />\n沙田有人用雪糕桶扔警犬先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗對住警犬起防線 和平個時<br />\n<br />\n所以想做和理非 其實做到 係睇手足想點做<br />\n<br />\n上環本身就勇武回合 不作評論"},{"pid":"4a55179e0c1bf66b43b1dabe4885ddf8ddab4738","tid":1395992,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OosJYdV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOosJYdV.png&h=a67965ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f408b1ec1c06ba57126e84b4e4a96bc0cf98dda8","tid":1395992,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fa9287033e62186872448764d6bf63580a0eab11","tid":1395992,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a96a79d54793205871f7de943b4d5e4655bf9a8e","tid":1395992,"uid":285899,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"同意轉返做和理非回合一段時間<br />\n就算勇武都要有目標 sosad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f50fe7b5fc2ae596818a0adc6e8042b88d0de05","tid":1395992,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"最大問題係如果話勇武製造衝突畫面丶突顯黑警暴力鎮壓市民嘅話<br />\n<br />\n市民睇催淚彈同橡膠子彈睇到麻目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔再有好似612咁震驚嘅效果<br />\n就好似612放催淚彈都冇5年前928咁震撼<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲嚟講，如果一個人食2個蘋果就飽嘅話<br />\n比3個蘋果佢佢會好感恩<br />\n4個佢會超開心<br />\n但5個、6個嘅疊加效應就少得多<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多次衝突加上721<br />\n要覺得政府垃圾、黑警濫權嘅人一早就覺醒左<br />\n其他嘅再俾佢睇咩暴力鎮壓畫面佢都會無動於衷<br />\n<br />\n黑心啲講句，下一個心理關口已經去到有人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee28600f5b291dc217c251819bcbfe753965c65","tid":1395992,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"a30279271a4f1afdaf8db68d6b755681a7a10ca0","tid":1395992,"uid":271351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"贊成暫時要和理非，至少今個星期六日都要，畫面上唔好嚇怕準備星期一出來罷工既人<br />\n<br />\n之後如果武勇可唔可以hit &amp; run?"},{"pid":"18e11184269d08867439c39abe30603b2e6fcd14","tid":1395992,"uid":157037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"同意~間歇性咁玩!"},{"pid":"a5c812935390a1c74233579c1a42b975e5cc9d2d","tid":1395992,"uid":286685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a30279271a4f1afdaf8db68d6b755681a7a10ca0","tid":1395992,"uid":271351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"贊成暫時要和理非，至少今個星期六日都要，畫面上唔好嚇怕準備星期一出來罷工既人<br />\n<br />\n之後如果武勇可唔可以hit &amp; run?"},"citedBy